{{Infobox dungeon |name = Aether Foundation |image = [[File:Aether Foundation.png|300px]] |caption = A map of Aether Foundation. |tokens = 1,080,000 |location = North of Aether Paradise }}
'''Aether Foundation''' is a [[Dungeons|dungeon]] in [[Alola]]. It initially has 121 tiles arranged in a 11x11 square, including 11 chest tiles, 41 non-boss encounter tiles, and 1 boss encounter tile. Wild Encounters have 15,619,682 HP.
